Class ArrayQueue

java.lang.Object
  dataStructures.ArrayQueue
All Implemented Interfaces:
Collection, Queue
Direct Known Subclasses:
ArrayDeque
public class ArrayQueue
extends java.lang.Object
implements Queue

ArrayQueue class implementation of an array-based queue the implementation uses a circular array to allow efficient utilization of the space in the array Written by Roger West, University of Illinois at Springfield Adapted from code written by Mark Weiss in Data Structures and Problem Solving Using Java, 2nd edition, 2002
